== Usage ==
<pre>{{StylishQuote/Draft |user= |link= |quote=}}</pre>

[[File:Comment-permalink-howto.png|700px]]

=== User ===
The name of the user you are quoting it from. Defaults to [[User:Default]] if unspecified.

=== Link ===
The full link minus the part after (and including) the literal question mark (?) from where the user has made the statement. Defaults to static "wrote:" phrase if unspecified.

=== Quote ===
The quoted statement to include. If line breaks were used by the quoted user, you can use <br> to make line breaks as needed. Shows nothing if unspecified.